	<key>readme</key>
	<string>Alfred Paste Workflow

Type 'p' followed by a transformation verb to transform your clipboard content:
- psort: Sort lines alphabetically
- preverse: Reverse line order
- pupper: Convert to uppercase
- plower: Convert to lowercase
- ptrim: Trim whitespace from lines

The transformed content will be automatically pasted.</string>
